title: Beautiful 2 bedroom home available now! Cats & Dogs welcome!

posting_body: ['Well appointed floorplans await you and your four legged friends!', 'Beautiful 3rd floor 2 bedroom unit, recently updated, stainless steel appliances, wall to wall closet space, large balconies and private garages available to rent.', 'Strategically located just 5 minutes away from the Maplewood Mall, Costco Wholesale, and countless restaurants within a 10-minute drive!', 'Walking/Biking path within 2 blocks that connects with The Gateway Trail', 'Within walking distance from Lake Gervais and Lake Kohlman, as well as a playground a block away!', 'Perfect for commuting, you can jump onto I35E, I694, and Highway 36 within minutes.', 'Application 45 per adult, $400 pre-lease deposit, deposit 1175', 'Pet rent for dogs $50 per month, Cats $25 per month', 'Give us a call at', 'show contact info', 'to ask about even more reasons as to why you should schedule your personal showing today!', 'Apply directly on our website at <URL>, you will need to copy and paste the link into your web browser']
